    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Organized undead thralls under the command of the Wyrd-Draugr. They move in formation and carry tools and equipment eastward through the cave system. When directed, they fight with much greater coordination than normal wandering draugr.</p>",
      "director": "<p><strong>ABILITIES</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Clawed Swipe</strong> (Main, Melee, Might): T1 1 dmg; T2 2 dmg; T3 4 dmg.</li></ul><p><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Fragile:</strong> Bane on Might saves vs. being moved.</li><li><strong>Mindless:</strong> Immune to fear and charm effects.</li></ul><p>Group of 6. Beat 12 (with Wyrd-Draugr). EV 6 total platoon.</p>",
